    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在欠下了工作一辈子也还不完的债务后，你被迫接受了一个神秘的邀请，参与到一场赌局中。你可以在牌桌上步步为营，或者借助其它手段还清你的债务，并逐步发掘隐藏在赌局背后的秘密。你最好小心行事，失败的代价并非任何人都能承受。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >简约而不简单的牌局</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验一系列精心设计的对局，赢取筹码抵消债务，离开牢笼重获自由。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233960/extras/5017af06d14c5f730f8ae75c8ff274be.avif?t=1737084540\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233960/extras_big/5017af06d14c5f730f8ae75c8ff274be.avif?t=1737084540 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233960/extras/4f3dd4bb2df31aee1a8f7ee462bc3ee2.avif?t=1737084540\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233960/extras_big/4f3dd4bb2df31aee1a8f7ee462bc3ee2.avif?t=1737084540 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多套全新的纸牌对局规则</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >强化心理博弈</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沉浸式体验</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >微型经济系统</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >管理你的资产，购买道具让你在赌桌上取得更大优势，或是投身进入更大的赌局——股票和赌马。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233960/extras/9adf44514db89790494a3f6fad05e974.avif?t=1737084540\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233960/extras_big/9adf44514db89790494a3f6fad05e974.avif?t=1737084540 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233960/extras/7f39cc578590fd82685292ea071cb2cc.avif?t=1737084540\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233960/extras_big/7f39cc578590fd82685292ea071cb2cc.avif?t=1737084540 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233960/extras/c0407f59ed3bd8f39664fa1aadbcbc7b.avif?t=1737084540\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233960/extras_big/c0407f59ed3bd8f39664fa1aadbcbc7b.avif?t=1737084540 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >商品价格动态变化的市场</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与市场波动相关联的股票</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >抽奖机和赌马场</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >发掘故事的真相</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择清空你的债务就此脱身，亦或是在囚笼中探索，逐步了解赌局背后埋藏的黑暗秘密。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233960/extras/4cddb3932e14a08e4fbb4f5cb04fc257.avif?t=1737084540\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233960/extras_big/4cddb3932e14a08e4fbb4f5cb04fc257.avif?t=1737084540 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >和朋友们一起玩</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >创建线上联机牌局，选择自己的对战风格，和朋友们一起体验游戏乐趣。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233960/extras/0b9c7b4c86b3a17c959d6b6a370147c8.avif?t=1737084540\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233960/extras_big/0b9c7b4c86b3a17c959d6b6a370147c8.avif?t=1737084540 width=800 height=450 /></span></p>",
